articles.author: Will Freeman
articles.title: Erik ten Hag steps up Harry Kane interest with fresh Man Utd transfer plan - The Mirror
articles.description: Harry Kane is top of Manchester United's shortlist of players to sign this summer, with Erik ten Hag expected to be in the market for a striker amid the club's impending takeover
articles.content: Manchester United are expected to step up their efforts to sign Harry Kane this summer, with the Tottenham striker believed to be top of a shortlist of three strikers who will be targeted for a move.… [+2630 chars]
